
Description
-----------
 - Program creates 5 threads.
 - Each thread increments global variable and uses binary semaphore for synchronization.

Steps to run the program:
-------------------------

 1. make
 It will generate a executable file thread.

 2. make clean
 Removes executable file thread.

 3. ./thread
 Runs executable thread.

OUTPUT
-------
 glb_var=1  TID=47861715482368
 glb_var=2  TID=47861717583616
 glb_var=3  TID=47861713381120
 glb_var=4  TID=47861719684864
 glb_var=5  TID=47861721786112


Note: TID(THREAD ID) will be different during each run.
